12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 36 O.S. 2021, Section 3634.3, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 3634.3. A. A health insurance plan or policy or health
16 maintenance organization providing prescription drugs as a covered
17 benefit shall provide a pharmacy or group of pharmacies with the
18 right to bid on a periodic basis, but not less than every three (3)
19 years, on any pharmacy contract to provide pharmacy services,
20 including, but not limited to, prescription drugs.
21 B. A health insurance plan or policy or health maintenance
22 organization providing prescription drugs as a covered benefit shall
23 notify its customers in writing at least thirty (30) days in advance
24 of renewal of the insured's insurance premium if the health
