4 C. Nothing in this act shall be interpreted to preclude a
5 health insurance plan or policy or health maintenance organization
6 from establishing an open pharmacy network for the provision of
7 pharmacy services, including, but not limited to, prescription
8 drugs.
9 C. D. The provisions of this section shall not apply to a
10 health insurance plan or policy or health maintenance organization
11 that maintains an open pharmacy network.
12 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
